This project contains phonetic annotations derived from the CoVox dataset.

Original dataset:
CoVox – A dataset of contrasting vocalizations
Authors: Camila Bruder, Nicolas Larrouy-Maestri
Institution: Max Planck Institute for Empirical Aesthetics

Phonetic system:
CatIPA, developed by Catmon

This repository does not include the original audio files.
Users must obtain CoVox data from the original source.

